❌ Permission denied
❌ Could not read
❌ Unable to create
❌ did not match
❌ refusing to merge
```

### 🟡 警告・注意の証拠リスト

```bash
⚠️ warning:
⚠️ hint:
⚠️ (MERGING)
⚠️ detached HEAD
⚠️ diverged
⚠️ behind
⚠️ ahead
⚠️ Unmerged paths
⚠️ both modified
⚠️ LF will be replaced by CRLF
```

